title: Ep 2749 - The Milk Conundrum Continues
shortDesc: Atmaram Bhide is shocked because someone stole milk from all the society members and they had to buy milk from Abdul's shop. He thinks Abdul has stolen the milk.

title: Ep 2750 - Milk Thievery
shortDesc: Iyer gets caught while opening the storehouse where the milk is stored, gets beaten but later he claims that he has not stolen any milk and he has something to say. Everybody eagerly waits for his statement. Stay tuned to know more!

title: Ep 2751 - Sting Operation
shortDesc: The men gang find out who is stealing the milk and they spy on what has been happening. They plan to invade and confront them and bring the truth out in the open. Stay tuned!

title: Ep 2752 - Bhide Offers To Teach For Free
shortDesc: Bhide tells Tappu and his friends that as much hard work a student does for his studies, the same amount of hard work a teacher does to teach his students.

title: Ep 2753 - Jethalals Delhi Trip
shortDesc: Jethalal is ready for a Delhi trip and his father comes to his room to check whether he has packed everything or not. Even he asks him to set his alarm so that he won't miss the flight. Stay tuned to know more!

title: Ep 2754 - Water Plight In Gokuldham Society
shortDesc: Iyer is able to wash his hair after a tedious search for water. Meanwhile, Mr. Mehta, Popatlal and Sodhi try to find the solution to the water crisis. Will they be able to fetch water? Keep watching to know.

title: Ep 2755 - Every Drop Of Water Counts
shortDesc: Bhide along with others come to know after an enquiry that the water crisis has no instant remedy. Everyone is desperate now for even a drop. Keep watching to know what's next.

title: Ep. 2756 - Water Crisis Continues  - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah - 19 June 2019
shortDesc: Amid the ruckus for water in society, everyone is waiting for the tanker to arrive. Meanwhile, Goli comes home smeared with mud. There seems no way out. Stay tuned!

title: Ep. 2757 - Waterless Gokuldham Society - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah - 20 June 2019
shortDesc: Due to the unavailability of water, people in society arrange to eat outside. Amid all these adjustments, the water tanker arrives for which the entire locality was waiting for. Who will get water and who won't? Keep watching!

title: Ep. 2758 - Mission Find Water - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah - 21 June 2019
shortDesc: All the members of Gokuldham society try searching for water everywhere but find themselves unsuccessful. They keep on finding water in different places and finally, Champaklal scolds Iyer for the same. Stay tuned to know more!

title: Ep. 2759 - Water To Come Soon - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah - 24 June 2019
shortDesc: Everybody in the society are relying on alternatives for solving the water issue. Meanwhile, Bhide, Sodhi and Popatlal go to the municipality water supply to know that water will arrive next morning. Keep watching!

title: Ep. 2760 - Water On High Demand - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah - 25 June 2019
shortDesc: After getting false hopes from the municipality water supply, people in the society look forward to order a water tanker but Champaklal opposes. What will they do now? Stay tuned!

title: Ep. 2761 - Water Problem Solved - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah - 26 June 2019
shortDesc: After people in society decide to abandon the place due to the water crisis, suddenly there is rainfall. Everybody is delighted now as the water problem is solved. Stay tuned!

title: Ep. 2762 - New Admission - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah - 27 June 2019
shortDesc: Bhide prepares for the first day of tuition classes. He tells Madhavi that he has lots of work to do today. A new kid takes admission in Bhide's tuition classes, but his parents think that Bhide is the watchman of Gokuldham society. Stay tuned!

title: Ep. 2763 - Bhide's Tution Board - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah - 28 June 2019
shortDesc: Bhide is too much possessive about his board he has hung for his tuition classes. Tappu, while playing football with his friends hits the board down to the ground. The board now is broken. Keep watching!
